<p sourcefile="includes/mvc-intro/adding-model3.md" sourcestartlinenumber="23" sourceendlinenumber="23">Create a couple more movie entries. Try the <strong>Edit</strong>, <strong>Details</strong>, and <strong>Delete</strong> links, which are all functional.</p>
